OL,3,GOPINIONCLittle information about STV cuts -
OL,4,Cbut what are the options?
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt is reported that the company wants
OL,7,Fto cut 60 jobs including 30 in news.
OL,9,FNothing appears to have been said
OL,10,Fpublicly to clarify just what roles are
OL,11,Ffacing the axe. Are all the job cuts in
OL,12,FAberdeen?
OL,14,FNor has anything been said publicly to
OL,15,Fconfirm what the new programme would
OL,16,Flook like.
OL,18,FSTV has just spent good money revamping
OL,19,Fthe look of its news service.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
