OL,3,GOPINIONCLittle information about STV cuts -
OL,4,Cbut what are the options?
OL,5,
OL,6,FMy guess is we might end up with the
OL,7,Fcurrent Central Belt programme with
OL,8,Fsome stories from the north of Scotland
OL,9,Fwithin the mix.
OL,11,FIt will not feel obviously different to
OL,12,Fviewers in Glasgow and Edinburgh.
OL,14,FThe proposed changes have been widely
OL,15,Fcondemned by politicians in the north
OL,16,Fof Scotland.
OL,18,FBut will Ofcom - if it is so minded -
OL,19,Fsave Grampian?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
