OL,3,GOPINIONCLittle information about STV cuts -
OL,4,Cbut what are the options?
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt is possible they will reject STV's
OL,7,Fplan outright. Past experience though
OL,8,Fsuggests this is unlikely. It would
OL,9,Falso be humiliating for STV management.
OL,11,FRealistically they'll either say yes or
OL,12,Fbroker some compromise. Perhaps
OL,13,Fpre-recorded localised bulletins
OL,14,Fat1.55pm and 10.30pm plus a
OL,15,Fpre-recorded sub-opt within the 6pm
OL,16,Fprogramme. (At the weekend both regions
OL,17,Fget a joint bulletin from Glasgow.)
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
