OL,3,GOPINIONCLittle information about STV cuts -
OL,4,Cbut what are the options?
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut I cannot see Ofcom insisting that
OL,7,Fany remaining programme for the north
OL,8,Fneeds to be presented from Aberdeen.
OL,10,FThey cannot be inconsistent with what
OL,11,Flicensees are or are not allowed to do.
OL,12,FThink Border from Gateshead,
OL,13,FWestcountry from Bristol, the East
OL,14,FMidlands from Birmingham.
OL,16,FI don't think, however, that a
OL,17,Fcompletely recorded programme would be
OL,18,Fright or practical.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
