OL,3,GOPINIONCLittle information about STV cuts -
OL,4,Cbut what are the options?
OL,5,
OL,6,FSTV North does show some Scottish
OL,7,Fnational news, especially politics. A
OL,8,F5pm recording would mean a much poorer
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,FBut a 10-minute recorded section within
OL,12,Fthe programme focused on regional news
OL,13,Fcould work - even if it might be
OL,14,Fundesirable. Big stories or developing
OL,15,Fstories can go in the live part of the
OL,16,Fprogramme.
