OL,3,GOPINIONCLittle information about STV cuts -
OL,4,Cbut what are the options?
OL,5,
OL,6,FOfcom's consultation should reveal more
OL,7,Fdetails of the plan plus the possible
OL,8,Ftimescale for a decision and, if
OL,9,Fagreed, changes.
OL,11,FThe public needs to be fully involved
OL,12,Fin this consultation.
OL,14,FIt needs information on STV's financial
OL,15,Fand strategic rationale as well as
OL,16,Fdetails of what the new programme might
OL,17,Fbe like.
