OL,3,GOPINIONCLittle information about STV cuts -
OL,4,Cbut what are the options?
OL,5,
OL,6,FOf course the changes are never going
OL,7,Fto be anything other than
OL,8,Fcontroversial.
OL,10,FBut full details are needed before
OL,11,Fsomeone can decide whether to accept
OL,12,Fthem with a heavy heart or argue for
OL,13,Fother ways of saving money instead.
